Thank you for installing CraigsForce, enterprise classified ads made easy.
<p/>
CraigsForce allows all users in an organization to post ads to buy, sell, give away, borrow, or trade goods.  
Although users may not know each other personally, there is a very high trust factor among users in the same organization, making it much safer than posting anonymous classified ads on public websites.
<p/>
