<h1>Customizing Categories (optional)</h1>
<p/>
CraigsForce comes with a set of preconfigured categories, but you are free to customize the categories for your organization.  To customize the categories:
<ol>
<li> Select <b>Setup | Create | Objects | Post | Category</b>.
<li> From there, you may edit, delete, or add new categories.
<li> When you are finished, select <b>Setup | Develop | Apex Classes</b>.
<li> Select <b>Edit</b> next to <b>PostingCategoryMapping</b>.
<li> This apex class lists the categories that are associated with prices.  Update this list based on the changed you made to the list of Categories in the prior steps.
<li> Save the class.  Return to the Posts tab and you should see your updated list of categories.

